rows.label: qst701508_msg0001
rows.name:
Phew! I really thought the grim reaper
was coming for me this time.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0002
rows.name: Whoa, there. Are you OK standing up?

rows.label: qst701508_msg0003
rows.name:
You should probably take it easy,
old man.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, don't worry about me! I feel much
better now, thanks to you.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0005
rows.name:
I have these funny turns sometimes.
But I just need a little rest and I'm right
as rain!

rows.label: qst701508_msg0006
rows.name:
You should absolutely get some rest.
But you should know you have a visitor.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0007
rows.name: A visitor? You mean a guest at the inn?

rows.label: qst701508_msg0008
rows.name:
Oh, blast! That means they've been
waiting all this time. I have to hurry
back!

rows.label: qst701508_msg0009
rows.name:
Hey! You can't go running off on your
own again!

rows.label: qst701508_msg0011
rows.name: Wadatsumi, come with me. We need you.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0013
rows.name:
You really wouldn't think he was lying
helpless on the ground two seconds
ago!

rows.label: qst701508_msg0014
rows.name:
He's young in spirit.
Not a bad thing at all.

rows.label: qst701508_msg0015
rows.name: It is a bit worrying, though, isn't it?

rows.label: qst701508_msg0016
rows.name:
Well, we came here to help, so we'll
just have to do that.
